ideya |title=(国指定史跡事典) National Historic Site Encyclopedia |date=2012 |publisher=学生社 |isbn=4311750404}}{{in lang|ja}}</ref> The grave goods designated are a Saga Prefectural Tangible Cultural Property. <ref name="Bunka2">{{cite web |url=https://www.pref.saga.lg.jp/kiji0031524/|title=佐賀文化財 database|language=ja |publisher=Saga Prefecture |accessdate=December 20, 2023}}</ref>
The tumulus is about a 25-minute walk from [[Hamasaki Station]] on the [[JR Kyushu]] [[Chikuhi Line]].<ref name="Shiseki"/>
